ist in the following format: <strong>&lt;ul class="</strong><em class="normal">list-icon twitter</em><strong>"&gt;&lt;li&gt;....&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;....&lt;/li&gt;...&lt;/ul&gt; (HTML)</strong>.</li>\r\n    <li>To use this style create a list in the following format: <strong>&#91;list class="<em class="normal">list-icon twitter</em>"&#93;&#91;li&#93;...&#91;/li&#93;&#91;li&#93;...&#91;/li&#93;&#91;/list&#93; (ROKCANDY)</strong>.</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n  <br />\r\n  <ul class="list-icon youtube">\r\n    <li>To use this style create a list in the following format: <strong>&lt;ul class="</strong><em class="normal">list-icon youtube</em><strong>"&gt;&lt;li&gt;....&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;....&lt;/li&gt;...&lt;/ul&gt; (HTML)</strong>.</li>\r\n    <li>To use this style create a list in the following format: <strong>&#91;list class="<em class="normal">list-icon youtube</em>"&#93;&#91;li&#93;...&#91;/li&#93;&#91;li&#93;...&#91;/li&#93;&#91;/list&#93; (ROKCANDY)</strong>.</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n  <br />\r\n  <ul class="list-icon skype">\r\n    <li>To use this style create a list in the following format: <strong>&lt;ul class="</strong><em class="normal">list-icon skype</em><strong>"&gt;&lt;li&gt;....&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;....&lt;/li&gt;...&lt;/ul&gt; (HTML)</strong>.</li>\r\n    <li>To use this style create a list in the following format: <strong>&#91;list class="<em class="normal">list-icon skype</em>"&#93;&#91;li&#93;...&#91;/li&#93;&#91;li&#93;...&#91;/li&#93;&#91;/list&#93; (ROKCANDY)</strong>.</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n  <br />\r\n  <ul class="list-icon facebook">\r\n    <li>To use this style create a list in the following format: <strong>&lt;ul class="</strong><em class="normal">list-icon facebook</em><strong>"&gt;&lt;li&gt;....&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;....&lt;/li&gt;...&lt;/ul&gt; (HTML)</strong>.</li>\r\n    <li>To use this style create a list in the following format: <strong>&#91;list class="<em class="normal">list-icon facebook</em>"&#93;&#91;li&#93;...&#91;/li&#93;&#91;li&#93;...&#91;/li