(91, 'About the Photographer', '<div class="rg-gm-slice floatleft"><img src="images/stories/launcher/photo1.jpg" border="0" alt="Image" width="96" height="96" /></div>\r\n<p>My galleries mainly feature images from my favourite destinations in <a href="#">the Americas and Europe</a>, featuring spectacular landscapes.</p>\r\n<p><a class="readon" href="#"><span>Contact Details</span></a></p>', 3, 'footer-a', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 'mod_custom', 0, 0, 1, 'moduleclass_sfx=\n\n', 0, 0, ''),
(92, 'Demo Information', '<p>\r\n	<em class="bold">DEMO NOTICE:</em> All demo content is for sample purposes only, intended to represent a live site. A stripped down version of the demo, including RokGallery is available for download.\r\n</p>', 4, 'footer-a', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 'mod_custom', 0, 0, 1, 'moduleclass_sfx=nopaddingleft\n\n', 0, 0, ''),
(94, 'FP MainBottom A', '<span class="icon-title">Navigation</span>\r\n<span class="icon-desc">Fusion &amp; Splitmenu</span>\r\n<a href="#" class="nobold">Two menu options</a>: the javascript enhanced CSS dropdown Fusion with MegaMenu features; and the venerable, static SplitMenu.', 3, 'mainbottom-a', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 'mod_custom', 0, 0, 0, 'moduleclass_sfx=icon1\n\n', 0, 0, ''),
(95, 'FP MainBottom B', '<span class="icon-title">Advanced Layout</span>\r\n<span class="icon-desc">Over 70 Module Positions</span>\r\nGantry''s advanced grid system allows for dynamic, <a href="#" class="nobold">flexible layouts, configurable</a> on a per menu item basis for true control.', 2, 'mainbottom-b', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 'mod_custom', 0, 0, 0, 'moduleclass_sfx=icon2\n\n', 0, 0, ''),
(96, 'FP MainBottom C', '<span class="icon-title">User Interface</span>\r\n<span class="icon-desc">Gantry Framework</span>\r\nGantry makes configuration a simple, quick and easy task, with its rich and <a href="#" class="nobold">dynamic control panel</a> for a range of template options.', 1, 'mainbottom-c', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 'mod_custom', 0, 0, 0, 'moduleclass_sfx=icon4\n\n', 0, 0, ''),
(97, 'FP MainBottom D', '<span class="icon-title">Styled Addons</span>\r\n<span class="icon-desc">RocketTheme Extensions</span>\r\nBeyond RokGallery, Reflex is <a href="#" class="nobold">bundled with a selection</a> of styled RocketTheme extensions, such as RokTabs &amp; RokTwittie', 1, 'mainbottom-d', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 'mod_custom', 0, 0, 0, 'moduleclass_sfx=icon3\n\n', 0, 0, ''),
(98, 'FP Sidebar A', '<h2 class="title largemargintop">Video Documentation</h2>\r\n<span class="desc">Introduction to RokGallery.</span>\r\n<img src="images/stories/launcher/video1.jpg" alt="image" />\r\n<p><strong>RokGallery</strong>, is a new gallery extension, with flexible, <strong>modern</strong> and powerful features. Introduce yourself to the basics with this <strong>short video</strong>.</p>\r\n<a href="http://demo.rockettheme.com/jul11/extensions/styled-addons/rokgallery" class="readon"><span>Learn More</span></a>', 6, 'sidebar-a', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 'mod_custom', 0, 0, 0, 'moduleclass_sfx=fp-feature nomarginbottom nopaddingbottom\n\n', 0, 0, ''),
(99, 'FP MainTop A', '<h2 class="title">Innovative Galleries</h2>\r\n<span class="desc">Custom tag-based architecture.</span>\r\n<img src="images/stories/launcher/blank1.png" alt="image" />\r\n<p><strong>Tagging</strong> allows a single image to be individualized across several <strong>galleries</strong>, by using multiple image tags, with each <strong>slice</strong> containing unique data.</p>\r\n<a href="index.php?option=com_rokgallery&amp;view=gallery&amp;Itemid=12" class="readon"><span>Continue Reading</span></a>', 2, 'maintop-a', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 'mod_custom', 0, 0, 0, 'moduleclass_sfx=fp-feature\n\n', 0, 0, ''),
(100, 'FP MainTop B', '<h2 class="title">File Uploader</h2>\r\n<span class="desc">HTML drag &amp; drop uploading.</span>\r\n<img src="images/stories/launcher/blank2.png" alt="image" />\r\n<p>Uploading new images to <strong>RokGallery</strong> is simple with its <strong>HTML5/Flash</strong> drag and drop uploader, with a conventional file browser alternative.</p>\r\n<a href="index.php?option=com_rokgallery&amp;view=gallery&amp;Itemid=12" class="readon"><span>Continue Reading</span></a>', 1, 'maintop-b', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 'mod_custom', 0, 0, 0, 'moduleclass_sfx=fp-feature\n\n', 0, 0, ''),
(101, 'FP MainTop C', '<h2 class="title">Image Editing</h2>\r\n<span class="desc">Modify using the Slice Editor.</span>\r\n<img src="images/stories/launcher/blank3.png" alt="image" />\r\n<p>The advanced <strong>Slice Editor</strong> is loaded with native application functionality such as <strong>non-destructive</strong> selective cropping and <strong>resizing</strong>.</p>\r\n<a href="index.php?option=com_rokgallery&amp;view=gallery&amp;Itemid=12" class="readon"><span>Continue Reading</span></a>', 1, 'maintop-c', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 'mod_custom', 0, 0, 0, 'moduleclass_sfx=fp-feature\n\n', 0, 0, ''),
(102, 'FP Footer C', '<p>Learn more about what RokGallery offers, and how to use its <a href="#">simple and intuitive user interface</a>,  by reading its introductory documentation below:</p>\r\n<a href="index.php?option=com_rokgallery&amp;view=gallery&amp;Itemid=12" class="readon"><span>More Information</span></a>', 3, 'footer-c', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 'mod_custom', 0, 0, 0, 'moduleclass_sfx=nopaddingright nomargintop nopaddingtop\n\n', 0, 0, ''),
